{"tid":2118019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修工去年立法會外搬鐵馬　判囚4個月","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T08:23:36.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cec127076d192309465c2ae95368760e276eece1","tid":2118019,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"一名裝修工人承認去年6月10日，在金鐘立法會示威區參與非法集結，今日在東區裁判法院以參與非法集結罪，被判監禁4個月。<br />\n33歲被告吳浩榮，去年6月9日反修例大遊行結束後，與約200名示威者繼續在立法會大樓外聚集，拆下圍封示威區的圍欄，未有理會警方警告，繼續搬動鐵欄，被告更將鐵馬搬到警方防線，隨即被制服。辯方律師求情說，被告的背景及社會服務令報告大致正面，不過有酗酒問題，因此不適合判處社會服務令，被告已承諾戒酒。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又說，被告認罪後已還柙多於3星期，他在本案中幾乎沒有使用暴力，希望法庭予以輕判。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但裁判官強調，暴力情況應視乎整體而言。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539042-20200721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539042-20200721.htm&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6Eelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=4855fa1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539042-20200721.htm&h=407bbd06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539042-20200721.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d9d5ff32869bd5cf0b6c0574cf5a48a0f1e4ea15","tid":2118019,"uid":34811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"錢禮依家判得好重"},{"pid":"7080aa278517c96ca02dbe86a2f1e8445b71d6cf","tid":2118019,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"點對付班狗官"},{"pid":"ac73c93f3af919d6836a111a3fd7ae9faf4fef43","tid":2118019,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"殺人情況視乎中華民族整體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dffda6c5bc7be7